---
import Container from "../ui/container.astro";
import TextWithTooltip from "../ui/text-with-tooltip.astro";
import Title from "../ui/title.astro";
import Separator from "../ui/separator.astro";
---

<div class="container">
  <Container>
    <Title>Hello World!</Title>
    <Separator />

    <p class="profile">
      I'm a software engineer deeply involved in <TextWithTooltip
        class="color-warning-lighter"
        tooltip="It's a programming language that is focused on performance and safety. It's used for systems programming, and building large, high-performance applications."
      >
        JavaScript
      </TextWithTooltip>, <TextWithTooltip
        class="color-success-lighter"
        tooltip="It's a statically typed superset of JavaScript that compiles to plain JavaScript. It's used for large-scale applications and transpiles to JavaScript."
      >
        TypeScript
      </TextWithTooltip>, and developing engaging applications with <TextWithTooltip
        class="color-success-lighter"
        tooltip="It's a JavaScript library for building user interfaces. It's used for building single-page applications and is maintained by Facebook."
      >
        ReactJS
      </TextWithTooltip>. I prioritize sleek visual design and performance
      optimization. My background includes <TextWithTooltip
        class="color-success-lighter"
        tooltip="It's a JavaScript framework for building native mobile applications. It's used for building cross-platform mobile applications and is maintained by Facebook."
      >
        React Native
      </TextWithTooltip>, and I'm currently enhancing my expertise with <TextWithTooltip
        class="color-warning-lighter"
        tooltip="It's a statically typed programming language that is focused on performance and safety. It's used for systems programming, and building large, high-performance applications."
      >
        Rust
      </TextWithTooltip>. Committed to continuous learning, I strive to stay at
      the forefront of technology advancements.
    </p>
  </Container>
</div>

<style>
  .container {
    --color-background: var(--color-accents-7);
    --color-foreground: var(--color-accents-1);

    padding: 4rem 0;
    background-color: var(--color-background);
    color: var(--color-foreground);
  }

  .profile {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-weight: 100;
    text-align: center;
    transition: var(--transition-animate);
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .title {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .container:hover .title {
    transform: translateY(-0.25rem);
  }

  .container:hover .profile {
    transform: translateY(0.25rem);
  }

  .container:hover [role="separator"] {
    width: 100rem;
  }
</style>
